<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Metro City Bus</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scrolling */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #f9f9f9; /* Added background color for consistency */
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        nav {
            background: #3b82f6;
            padding: 20px 10px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */
        }
        nav ul {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap; /* Ensure items wrap in case of smaller screens */
        }
        nav li {
            margin: 10px 10px; /* Ensure proper spacing on smaller screens */
        }
        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        main, header {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */
        }
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; /* Two equal columns */
            gap: 20px; /* Gap between items */
            align-items: center; /* Center items vertically */
        }
        .text {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in height calculation */
        }
        .image {
            text-align: center; /* Center image horizontally */
        }
        .image img {
            max-width: 100%; /* Ensure the image doesn't exceed its container */
            height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
            display: block; /* Remove any inline spacing issues */
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 10px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */
        }
        footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        footer a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        /* Tablet view (between 768px and 601px) */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Single column layout */
            }
            nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            nav li {
                display: block;
                margin: 5px 0;
            }
            nav a {
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }
        }
        /* Phone view (less than 600px) */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Single column layout */
            }
            nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            nav li {
                display: block;
                margin: 5px 0;
            }
            nav a {
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <% if (user) { %>
            <li><a href="/auth/logout">Log out</a></li>
            <% } else { %>
            <li><a href="/auth/login">Login</a></li>
            <% } %>
            <li><a href="/">Homepage</a></li>
            <li><a href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome To Metro City Bus Project</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text">
                <h2 class="tinCity">Tin City Metro Bus</h2>
                <p class="tinUrban">
                    The Tin City Metro Urban Transportation Initiative is aimed at mitigating the costs of
                    intra-city travel and providing a respite from the daily transportation challenges faced by commuters. It is more than a
                    transportation project; it is a catalyst for community
                    development. "These buses are not mere vehicles; they are mobile hubs of innovation, equipped with the latest amenities
                    such as Near Field Communication (NFC) and secure card payment systems. We are ushering in an era of digitised travel,
                    aligning with the global shift towards cashless transactions for the convenience of our passengers".
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="/images/metroBus(3).webp" alt="Metro Bus">
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Metro City Bus. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Contact us at <a href="">support@metrocitybus.com</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
